<tal:block tal:define="arglist python: context.getObject().DocumentationHelper_renderArgumentList()">
 <tal:block tal:condition="arglist">
 (
 <tal:block tal:repeat="mandatory python: arglist['mandatory']">
 <tal:block tal:replace="python: mandatory"/>
 <tal:block tal:condition="python: not(loop['mandatory'].end) or len(arglist['non_mandatory']) or arglist['*'] is not None or arglist['**'] is not None">, </tal:block>
 </tal:block>
 <tal:block tal:repeat="non_mandatory python: arglist['non_mandatory']">
 <tal:block tal:replace="python: '%s = %s' % (non_mandatory['name'], non_mandatory['value'])"/>
 <tal:block tal:condition="python: not(loop['non_mandatory'].end) or arglist['*'] is not None or arglist['**'] is not None">, </tal:block>
 </tal:block>
 <tal:block tal:condition="python: arglist['*'] is not None">
 *<tal:block tal:replace="python: arglist['*']"/>
 <tal:block tal:condition="python: arglist['**'] is not None">, </tal:block>
 </tal:block>
 <tal:block tal:condition="python: arglist['**'] is not None">
 **<tal:block tal:replace="python: arglist['**']"/>
 </tal:block>
 )
 </tal:block>
 </tal:block>
